It seems that when you go to trader mode you became a vendor and before the last patch, had all the attributes of a vendor.<br>
That meant that some enterprising rogue could have picked your pocket. There are reports of this happening.<br>
Also the theory was that someone could have gotten pps off you from begging also.<br>
<br>
Has anyone seen someone winning a ton of random rolls?<br>
The new UI allows you to do a /body set color insert text body and shoot out a tell that would look exactly like a random roll. This was caught by a guildee of mine on another server that was not using the new ui and saw this odd message sent out when they were randoming for an item. His wife was next to him on the new ui and he saw what was happening and reported it. This would also let someone send out a tell that looked like a system message telling everyone to exit, the zone is going down, and they could then move in and take over the camp after everyone else logged out.<br>
